# Le Verger du Coin Website

Welcome to the Le Verger du Coin website! This website allows users to place orders, view inventory, and manage loyal customers for a fruit store.

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
  - [Prerequisites](#prerequisites)
  - [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)
- [Acknowledgements](#acknowledgements)

## Features

- Place orders for various fruits.
- View and manage inventory.
- Keep track of loyal customers.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js and npm installed on your machine.
- MySQL database set up.

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/le-verger-du-coin.git
